<p>
In order to work with Ipfs, you need to setup an [ext[Http Api|https://docs.ipfs.io/reference/api/http/]] and an [ext[Http Gateway|https://github.com/ipfs/go-ipfs/blob/master/docs/gateway.md]] Url. 
</p>
<p>
The plugin eases the selection through drop-down lists.
</p>
<p>
<table>
<tr><th>Api Url</th><th>Tiddler</th></tr>
<tr><td>Default</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/api/default]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>http://127.0.0.1:5001</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/api/http/localhost/5001]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.bluelightav.org</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/api/https/ipfs.bluelightav.org]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.infura.io:5001</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/api/https/ipfs.infura.io/5001]]</td></tr>
</table>
</p>
<p>
  To enhance the Api Url drop-down list: 
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Clone an existing Api Url Tiddler (see above).</li>
  <li>Update the cloned Tiddler's name and update the [[Default Api Url Tiddler|$:/ipfs/saver/api/default]] if applicable.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<table>
<tr><th>Gateway Url</th><th>Tiddler</th></tr>
<tr><td>Default</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/default]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>http://ipfs.io</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/http/ipfs.io]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>http://127.0.0.1</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/http/localhost]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://cloudflare-ipfs.com</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/cloudflare-ipfs.com]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://gateway.ipfs.io</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/gateway.ipfs.io]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://gateway.pinata.cloud</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/gateway.pinata.cloud]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.bluelightav.org</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/ipfs.bluelightav.org]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.infura.io</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/ipfs.infura.io]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.io</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/ipfs.io]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://ipfs.jes.xxx</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/ipfs.jes.xxx]]</td></tr>
<tr><td>https://siderus.io</td><td>[[$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/https/siderus.io]]</td></tr>
</table>
</p>
<p>
  To enhance the Gateway Url drop-down list:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Clone an existing Gateway Url Tiddler (see above).</li>
  <li>Update the cloned Tiddler's name and the [[Default Gateway Url Tiddler|$:/ipfs/saver/gateway/default]] if applicable.</li>
</ul>
<p>
As a convenience here is a way to know the fastest available [ext[gateway|https://ipfs.github.io/public-gateway-checker/]].
</p>
